        <Parent_String>solar heating (systems) [300051512], heating systems [300051479], HVAC [300051474], systems by function [300242038], systems (equipment) [300008550], Object Groupings and Systems (hierarchy name) [300241489], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
